::Battera::

"Me? well, ah,..this is Battera.  I can try to get one of the 
maximals from the ship for you to talk to if you want."
She felt really nervious.  She wasn't sure who she was talking to, 
and she didn't know how they would react when they found out a 
Predacon answered the transmission.
